13
00:02:07,700 --> 00:02:09,330
Should I just stand by and watch him

14
00:02:09,330 --> 00:02:11,990
leave everything to Gu Manqing's two bastards?

15
00:02:12,500 --> 00:02:13,410
Or should it go to

16
00:02:13,410 --> 00:02:15,870
those disgraceful mistresses of his?

17
00:02:16,950 --> 00:02:17,829
Besides,

18
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:20,500
