20
00:02:26,290 --> 00:02:28,620
What will happen to you if this continues?

21
00:02:29,079 --> 00:02:30,540
Yuanying, listen to me.

22
00:02:30,829 --> 00:02:32,450
Now that you know,

23
00:02:32,870 --> 00:02:34,870
you and I are in this together.

24
00:02:34,950 --> 00:02:35,829
This matter

25
00:02:35,829 --> 00:02:38,450
cannot be revealed to anyone, not a single word.

26
00:02:38,450 --> 00:02:39,540
Otherwise,

27
00:02:39,540 --> 00:02:42,000
