28
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,370
Do you understand?

29
00:02:49,540 --> 00:02:50,500
Okay.

30
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,329
Even if not for me,

31
00:02:52,329 --> 00:02:53,500
not for yourself,

32
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:56,620
don't you care about Tong Hao's life anymore?

33
00:02:57,370 --> 00:02:59,770
