34
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:02,910
Yuanying.

35
00:03:03,750 --> 00:03:05,080
I'm sorry.

36
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:07,290
Yuanying, I didn't mean it that way.

37
00:03:07,750 --> 00:03:09,120
You're my child.

38
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:11,370
You're my flesh and blood.

39
00:03:11,370 --> 00:03:12,830
Would I ever harm you?

40
00:03:15,410 --> 00:03:16,290
But,

41
00:03:16,290 --> 00:03:18,750
I want you to put yourself in my shoes,

42
00:03:18,750 --> 00:03:20,750
