43
00:03:26,790 --> 00:03:28,700
Can you try to understand me?

44
00:03:39,250 --> 00:03:40,040
Forget it.

45
00:03:40,579 --> 00:03:41,380
Stop talking.

46
00:03:41,700 --> 00:03:43,100
You should go back first.

47
00:04:08,870 --> 00:04:09,790
Dr. Ars,

48
00:04:09,790 --> 00:04:11,190
