51
00:04:17,700 --> 00:04:18,829
Private condition?

52
00:04:18,950 --> 00:04:21,040
You're going to be the death of me, Yan Ran.

53
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:22,160
I've never heard of that.

54
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:22,830
Let me tell you.

55
00:04:22,830 --> 00:04:24,330
He can't have children.

56
00:04:24,330 --> 00:04:25,930
