59
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:28,700
I don't know.

60
00:04:28,700 --> 00:04:30,300
Or if there's any other ques-

61
00:04:35,830 --> 00:04:37,750
Dr. Ars, is there anything else to discuss?

62
00:04:37,750 --> 00:04:38,950
Why don't we talk in the study?

63
00:04:38,950 --> 00:04:40,210
No, Young Master Zeng.

64
00:04:40,250 --> 00:04:41,040
I'm terribly sorry,

65
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,700
but I have urgent matters to attend to today.

66
00:04:42,700 --> 00:04:43,700
Please excuse me.

67
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:58,950
From now on, except for me,

68
00:04:58,950 --> 00:05:01,010
don't stand so close to any other man.

69
00:05:04,620 --> 00:05:06,220
Why are you being so jealous?

70
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:25,160
Why did Father suddenly stop Huosang

71
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,760
