72
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,330
How would I know?

73
00:05:29,200 --> 00:05:31,250
This wasn't part of the plan either.

74
00:05:31,450 --> 00:05:33,710
You two were talking so closely just now.

75
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:37,230
Was that part of the plan?

76
00:05:45,790 --> 00:05:47,320
I have something to report.

77
00:05:47,870 --> 00:05:51,000
Our people followed the young miss all the way to Liyuan.

78
00:05:52,250 --> 00:05:53,040
Liyuan?

79
00:05:55,409 --> 00:05:58,450
I remember that day when we came back from the hospital.

80
00:05:58,450 --> 00:06:01,250
I also wish to bear children for my husband.

81
00:06:01,580 --> 00:06:04,120
I've consulted all the famous doctors in Yong City.

82
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:06,200
They all say I'm in excellent health

83
00:06:06,330 --> 00:06:08,860
